# DataHarvest environment variables
#
# API keys can be configured in two ways:
#   1. Through the web UI (Settings page) -- stored in config.json
#   2. By copying this file to .env and uncommenting the variables below
#
# IMPORTANT: config.json and .env both contain secrets and are gitignored.
# Never commit either file to version control. If you fork this repo,
# verify that .gitignore is intact before pushing.
#
# We recommend setting a spending limit on your LLM provider account
# to cap costs in case a key is accidentally exposed.

# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...
# GOOGLE_AI_API_KEY=...
# SERPAPI_KEY=...
